transcripts.text: Did you ever have one of those days where you're not sure if you want to commit suicide or genocide?  This news legitimately hurts my brain.  I just have to remind myself that all things are temporary, all things are fleeting, and that at most I've got another 40 years of this painful human existence to go through.  So I try to remind myself, none of this matters, Frylock.  None of this friggin' matters.

Thank you for watching.  If you like this program, then please head over to my Patreon page and set up a monthly donation.  It's your donations that keep this program running.  Also, if you would like, please rate, comment, subscribe, and share on various social media.
